room_title: Escape room "The Interrogation Room" by Cold War Escape Room in Daytona Beach
room_address: 455 S. Nova Rd., Ormond Beach, FL 32174
room_description: One of our CIA agents was captured by the KGB while performing a covert operation in Leningrad. He was last seen being escorted into a known KGB detention facility outside the city. Intelligence from our inside source states that our agent is missing from the interrogation room. You and your team will be inserted by our source on the inside to investigate and confirm if it is possible to escape the iron grip of the KGB.
